PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-334, which reappointed Lawrence Hanigan as Chairman of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc., revoking therefrom the words "Montreal, Quebec" and substituting therefor the words "St-Sauveur-des-Monts, Quebec".
